    "description": "深藏在古老地牢的阴影中，一只兔子跌入黑暗。四周环绕着无数骷髅，它必须鼓起勇气和智慧，击败敌人，找到逃离地牢的办法。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第1章 深暗洞穴</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/b1cffd6cedc8b460f0626771cb7f70b2.poster.avif?t=1725605986\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/b1cffd6cedc8b460f0626771cb7f70b2.webm?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/b1cffd6cedc8b460f0626771cb7f70b2.mp4?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你在一个深洞的中心醒来，周围几乎一片黑暗。你唯一能用的能力是微弱的跳跃。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第2章 地牢中的兔子</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/ec577ed9c9cdfad604c09f2d67cf6e36.poster.avif?t=1725605986\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/ec577ed9c9cdfad604c09f2d67cf6e36.webm?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/ec577ed9c9cdfad604c09f2d67cf6e36.mp4?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>你必须用灵巧的步伐穿越地牢，克服无数骷髅。这是一场小小的脚掌的大挑战。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >第3章 最终决斗</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/e2c796e5512a6ad6ac99ced2f4d065de.poster.avif?t=1725605986\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/e2c796e5512a6ad6ac99ced2f4d065de.webm?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088890/extras/e2c796e5512a6ad6ac99ced2f4d065de.mp4?t=1725605986\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在漫长而危险的地牢尽头，你将面对最终的敌人……",
